  "description": {
    "zh": "我这儿又有个非常有趣的任务。一位特别重要的人物联系了我们，想谈一笔交易。他希望我们清理灯塔岛周边区域的 PMC、当地Scav，以及水处理厂的 Rogue 和 他们的头儿——三狗。\n\n而这还只是任务的一部分。你是完成它的最佳人选。怎么样，准备好帮忙了吗？",
    "en": "I got something really interesting again. Very special person just contacted us for a deal. He wanted us to clean up the area outside the lighthouse island from the PMC operatives and local, and also the rogue USECs and their leaders at the water treatment plant.\n\nAnd just so you know, that wasn't the whole deal, just a part of it and you are the perfect one to do it. So are you ready to help?"
  },
